column5: Hey its been a while since I have been here.......im sure I rubbed a few the wrong way.......and I apologize for taking things a bit personal......for those who may remember, it was about a poster getting a light slamming over posting an out of season bass...........anyways.........cheers!
You must have good calices on your break fingers!  It was like watching a mini-carpumentary.
lol, suprisingly enough, no, I switch between thumb and fingers - thanks for checking the video out    cheers
